Azure Boards is a tool inside Azure DevOps that helps teams plan, track, and manage work.

Teams use it to keep track of:

  tasks
  
  bugs
  
  features
  
  user stories
  
  project progress
  
  who is working on what


Main Parts of Azure Boards

  Work Items

  Boards

  Backlogs

  Sprints

  Queries

  Dashboards

Azure Boards and GitHub

  That means a task in Azure Boards can be linked to:

    GitHub commits
    
    branches
    
    pull requests
    
    issues






